    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban multilevel marketing businesses",
        "additional_details": "MLMs often convince people to spend a lot of money, promising huge profits, which is often very exaggerated. On top of this, it can often cause strain between the individual and their friends and family as they are encouraged to sell to those first.\r\n \r\nMembers are often vulnerable and may be manipulated in to continuing to spend money, while also being encouraged to be slightly mysterious as to what they are doing and will often get angry if someone tries to warn them.",
        "background": "I would like the government to ban MLMs.",
